Over here.

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.165
I got this one over here.

00:02:08.165 --> 00:02:09.380
We got to bring
people in for this.

00:02:09.380 --> 00:02:09.880
Yeah.

00:02:09.880 --> 00:02:12.550
MARISHA RAY: Well, and
the Twitch algorithm

00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:17.860
is weird, not to out any of our
friends a Twitch or anything.

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:21.940
But when you only see the
concurrent number of viewers

00:02:21.940 --> 00:02:24.160
watching at a time,
that's a little hard

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.920
to gauge how many
people in total

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:30.040
are actually aware in
watching your show.

00:02:30.040 --> 00:02:32.860
So I think it wasn't until
the first New York Comic Con

00:02:32.860 --> 00:02:36.461
