having a line around the block,

00:02:36.461 --> 00:02:37.210
and we were like--

00:02:37.210 --> 00:02:37.735
TRAVIS WILLINGHAM: Oh, no.

00:02:37.735 --> 00:02:38.710
MARISHA RAY: Oh.

