people watch our show.

00:02:42.610 --> 00:02:45.700
I don't think that's accurate,
unless all 10,000 are here

00:02:45.700 --> 00:02:47.770
in New York City.

00:02:47.770 --> 00:02:49.780
So that took some
time to get used to.

00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:50.020
TRAVIS WILLINGHAM: What was it?

00:02:50.020 --> 00:02:51.370
It was like a comic
book store, and we're

00:02:51.370 --> 00:02:53.440
