I opened up like, wizard,
and I was like, nope.

00:06:24.620 --> 00:06:26.000
Calculus-- nope.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:26.867
No, thanks.

00:06:26.867 --> 00:06:27.450
I want an axe.

00:06:27.450 --> 00:06:28.321
Can I hit things?

00:06:28.321 --> 00:06:28.820
Cool.

00:06:28.820 --> 00:06:29.986
Just tell me as we go along.

00:06:29.986 --> 00:06:31.160
That's all I need to know.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:33.720
I watched the "Handbooker
Helper" videos and I'm like,

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:35.885
oh.

00:06:35.885 --> 00:06:36.860
But three years--

00:06:36.860 --> 00:06:38.318
MARISHA RAY: Six
years later, yeah.

00:06:38.318 --> 00:06:38.830
[LAUGHING]

